t=\"Orb of protection.png\" src=\"/images/Orb_of_protection.png?31c6a\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"14\" data-file-width=\"18\" data-file-height=\"14\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Orb_of_protection\" title=\"Orb of protection\">Orb of protection</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Orbs_of_protection\" title=\"Orbs of protection\"><img alt=\"Orbs of protection.png\" src=\"/images/Orbs_of_protection.png?31c6a\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"23\" height=\"15\" data-file-width=\"23\" data-file-height=\"15\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Orbs_of_protection\" title=\"Orbs of protection\">Orbs of protection</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Gnome_amulet\" title=\"Gnome amulet\"><img alt=\"Gnome amulet.png\" src=\"/images/Gnome_amulet.png?caa5a\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"26\" data-file-width=\"18\" data-file-height=\"26\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Gnome_amulet\" title=\"Gnome amulet\">Gnome amulet</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Locations</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Tree_Gnome_Village_(location)\" title=\"Tree Gnome Village (location)\">Tree Gnome Village</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Gnome_Maze\" title=\"Gnome Maze\">Gnome Maze</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Battlefield\" title=\"Battlefield\">Battlefield</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Miscellaneous</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Tree_Gnome_Village_(quest)/Quick_guide\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tree Gnome Village (quest)/Quick guide\">Quick Guide</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Spirit_tree\" title=\"Spirit tree\">Spirit tree</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Transcript:Tree_Gnome_Village\" title=\"Transcript:Tree Gnome Village\">Transcript</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐67df7655d‐sm4lh\nCached time: 20220420104136\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.107 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.129 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 652/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 34980/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1675/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2524/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.029/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1676037/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   75.538      1 -total\n 33.09%   24.999      4 Template:Navbox\n 20.38%   15.394      2 Template:CiteText\n 18.75%   14.163      1 Template:Battles\n 17.98%   13.582      1 Template:Tree_Gnome_Village\n 16.33%   12.332      1 Template:External\n 10.15%    7.666      1 Template:Infobox_War\n  8.80%    6.648      3 Template:CiteNPC\n  6.47%    4.884      1 Template:Reflist\n  5.95%    4.495      2 Template:Ctg\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:273723-0!canonical and timestamp 20220420104135 and revision id 14119544. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{External|rs=Khazard–Gnome War}}\n{{Infobox War\n|name = Khazard–Gnome War\n|begin = Late Fourth Age\n|end = Ongoing\n|place = Central [[Kandarin]] and [[Gnome Empire]]\n|outcome = Ongoing\n|battles = [[Battlefield|Battle of the Tree Gnome Village]]\n|combatant1 = [[Gnome Empire]]\n|combatant2 = Khazard's Army\n|commander1 = [[King Narnode Shareen]], [[King Bolren]]\n|commander2 = [[General Khazard]], [[Khazard Commander|Khazard Commander's]], [[Khazard warlord]]\n|casualties1 = Unknown, but believed to be very high\n|casualties2 = Unknown, but believed to be very high\n|concurrent = [[Arposandran War]]\n|previous =\n|next =\n}}\nThe '''Khazard–Gnome War''' is an ongoing military conflict between the Northern and Southern [[Gnome Empire]] and the forces of the [[Mahjarrat]] [[General Khazard]], centered at the [[Battlefield]]. The war is featured in the [[Gnome quest series]]. The cause of the war is currently unknown. However, it does appear that fighting between the gnomish and Khazard forces began in earnest due to killings carried out by the Khazard against the gnomes.{{CiteText|text=Glough's Journal|author=Glough|loc=The Grand Tree|page=2-3|quote=Today I heard of three more gnomes slain by Khazard's human troops for fun, I can't control my anger! ... We are small and at heart not warriors but something must be done! We will pick up arms and go forth into the human world! We will defend ourselves and we will pursue justice for all gnomes who fell at the hands of humans!}} These attacks themselves may have been in response to gnomish expansion into the region after the gnomes [[Gnome (race)#History of gnomes|emerged from underground]] following the end of the [[God Wars]].{{CiteText|text=Glough's Journal|loc=The Grand Tree|author=Glough|page=1-2|quote=However, rather than the great liberation promised to us by King Healthorg at the end of the last age, we have been forced to live in hiding up trees or in the gnome maze, laughed at and mocked by man. Living in constant fear of human aggression, we are in a no better situation now than when we lived in the caves!}}\n\n[[Tree Gnome Stronghold|At one point]] the Gnome army got desperate enough to send one of their [[Orb of protection|orbs of protection]] to the Battlefield.{{CiteNPC|npc=King Bolren|loc=Tree Gnome Stronghold|quote=We became desperate, so we took one orb of protection to the battlefield. It was a foolish move.}} However this left their Village vulnerable, and a group of Khazard soldiers managed to navigate the maze, attack the village (killing [[King Bolren]]'s wife and many other gnomes),{{CiteNPC|npc=King Bolren|loc=Tree Gnome Stronghold|quote=Khazard troops. They slaughtered anyone who got in their way. Women, children, my wife.}} and steal the other orbs.{{CiteNPC|npc=King Bolren|loc=Tree Gnome Stronghold|quote=They took the other orbs, now we are defenceless.}} An adventurer managed to recover the orbs, defeating a [[Khazard warlord]] who was in possession of one of the orbs.\n\nThe war coincides with the [[Arposandran War]], which is also a part of the gnome quest series.\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Battles}}\n{{Tree Gnome Village}}\n[[Category:Kandarin]]"}